|`ca-view-leaf` |filter |view (implicit-channel) |Optional leaf-test for the implicit channel. |
|`ca-view-label` |filter |view (implicit-channel) |Optional display-name override for the implicit channel. |
|`ca-view-row-entity-type` |filter |view (implicit-channel) |Optional per-row entity-type filter for the implicit channel. Right-arrow on a leaf with a non-empty type opens the action-menu stage of that type. |
