|`ca-channel-roots` |filter |channel |Filter producing root rows (no `<currentTiddler>` binding). |
|`ca-channel-children` |filter |channel |Filter producing direct children of `<currentTiddler>` (the parent). |
|`ca-channel-leaf` |filter |channel |Optional leaf-test (`<currentTiddler>` = candidate). |
|`ca-channel-label` |filter |channel |Optional display-name override (`<currentTiddler>` = node). |
|`ca-channel-row-name` / `-hint` / `-icon` / `-kind` / `-group` / `-order` |filter |channel |Per-row field overrides (`<currentTiddler>` = row). |
|`ca-channel-row-actions` |filter ''or'' wikitext |channel |Action fired on a leaf pick. Same dual-mode behaviour as `ca-view-row-actions`. |
|`ca-channel-row-entity-type` |filter |channel |Per-row entity-type filter. Returning a non-empty type on a leaf row makes Right-arrow open the action-menu stage of that type. |
|`ca-channel-row-next-scope` / `-items-from` |filter |channel |Per-row synthetic drill filter. |
|`ca-channel-include-position` |`yes`\|`no` |channel |Whether `ca-position` annotations apply to rows emitted by this channel. Default `yes`. |
|`ca-channel-preview` |tiddler title |channel |Names a wikitext tiddler shown as this channel's ''Overview'' summary in the side preview. At the root stage the channel emits one synthetic ''Overview'' row leading its group; focusing it renders the template, and ''Enter'' moves focus into the preview pane. The row is a non-drill no-op leaf, excluded from search, pinned to the top of its group. Subject to `ca-view-show-side-preview`. |
|`ca-channel-preview-name` |string |channel |Label for the Overview row + its preview pill. Default `Overview`. |
