|`ca-axis-sort` |`first-seen`\|`asc`\|`desc`\|`enum` |axis |Bucket sort policy. `first-seen` (default) preserves source insertion order; `asc` / `desc` localeCompare on key; `enum` reads `ca-axis-sort-keys`. |
