|`ca-row-icon-alt-action` |wikitext |row-icon |Optional ''secondary'' action fired by Ctrl-Alt-↵ on the row (in addition to Alt-↵'s primary action). Same variables: `<<payload>>` + `<<row-icon-key>>` + `<<row-icon-mode>>` (= `"alt"` when fired via Ctrl-Alt-↵) + standard stage vars. |
