|`ca-view-sort` |`alphabetical`\|`natural`\|`by-field`\|`custom` |view |Row sort policy; default `alphabetical`. `alphabetical` / `natural` sort by each row's ''displayed (lensed) name'' — the active name-lens / row-label result (e.g. the `caption`), not the raw title — so the visible order matches what the user reads. `natural` adds numeric-aware, case-insensitive collation. |
|`ca-view-sort-field` |string |view (by-field) |Field name read off each row |
|`ca-view-sort-key` |filter |view (custom) |Per-row filter returning a sortable key |
|`ca-view-containers-first` |`yes`\|`no` |view |Containers float above leaves at each tree level. Default `yes` for tree views |
