|`ca-view-preview-title` |string |view |Caption shown above the preview body. |
|`ca-view-row-name` / `-hint` / `-icon` / `-kind` / `-group` / `-order` / `-next-scope` / `-items-from` |filter |view |Per-source overrides; evaluated with `<currentTiddler>` bound to the source. Unset filters fall through to the source's own `ca-*` field |
