|`ca-lens-default` |slot list |lens |Space-separated slot names this lens seeds on first load when that slot has no `$:/state/rimir/cascade-palette/lens/<slot>` stored. Shipped as `name` on the ''Caption → Title'' lens so a fresh install shows captions uniformly across all views. |
|`ca-view-pick-emits-filter` |filter-title |view (pick-mode) |Filter tiddler whose `ca-filter-expr` receives the picked path as `<arg>` |
|`ca-leader-key` |string |leader |Trigger string (single char or short multi-char). Required. |
|`ca-leader-name` |string |leader |Display name (for catalogues / details rendering). |
|`ca-leader-hint` |string |leader |One-line hint shown in the footer during the idle window. |
|`ca-leader-help` |string (multiline) |leader |Help shown in the detail pane during the idle window. Falls back to hint. |
